        <description>&lt;div style=&#34;font-size: 16px; color: blue; font-weight: bold;&#34;&gt;
    资源封面
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;div align=&#34;center&#34; style=&#34;font-size: 12px; color: blue; font-weight: bold;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;img src=&#34;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siriforu/qiqi-pic/20251229095415349.jpg&#34;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
